page.title: 06TYPICAL DAY OF A 12YR. OLD
page.content: My school day usually starts at 7:30 am.I get up,dress and have breakfast at 8:00 am.While I am eating I watch breakfast television.At 8:30 I go to school.Lessons start at 9:00 am and end at 3:30 pm.We have 3 breaks. Lessons include maths,english,science, history and french.I get home and change into my jeans.I watch TV,I like cartoons best.I do my homewopk.My mum and dad come home from work at 6:00 pm,and then we have supper.Afterwards I watch more TV and go to bed at 9:00 pm. My friend John goes jogging before school,he jogs about 1\ miles.After school he likes to practice snooker and when he goes to bed he likes to read Roald Dahl and Enid Blyton.
